            "message": "<strong>Note:<\/strong> Partners are managed in the <a href=\"\/wp-admin\/edit.php?post_type=partners\" target=\"_blank\">Partners section<\/a>.<br><br><strong>Features:<\/strong><ul><li>Automatically queries all published partners<\/li><li>Category filtering with tabs (uses partner_category taxonomy)<\/li><li>Special 2-3-2-3 grid pattern for visual interest<\/li><li>Hover effects and smooth transitions<\/li><\/ul><strong>Responsive Behavior:<\/strong><ul><li><strong>Desktop:<\/strong> Alternating 2\/3 column pattern<\/li><li><strong>Tablet:<\/strong> 2 columns<\/li><li><strong>Mobile:<\/strong> 1 column<\/li><\/ul><strong>Partner Information Displayed:<\/strong><ul><li>Logo (featured image)<\/li><li>Company name (post title)<\/li><li>Description (excerpt or custom field)<\/li><li>Website link (external link)<\/li><li>Category tags (for filtering)<\/li><\/ul><strong>Category Filtering:<\/strong><ul><li>Tabs auto-generate from partner_category taxonomy<\/li><li>Smooth fade in\/out animation<\/li><li>\"All Partners\" shows everything<\/li><li>Click category tab to filter<\/li><\/ul>",
